victor joseph garber ( born march 16 , 1949 ) is a canadian film , stage , and television actor and singer . he is known for playing jesus in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , anthony hope in sweeney todd : the demon barber of fleet street , john wilkes booth in assassins , jack &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in the television series alias , max in lend me a tenor , thomas andrews in james cameron 's titanic , and ken taylor , canadian ambassador to iran , in argo . he is currently a series regular on legends of tomorrow as dr. martin stein , playing the same role as a guest star on the flash and the web series vixen .